.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt ORT-AUDIT-JSON 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ort-audit-json
.Nd audit ort role access as JSON
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm ort-audit-json
.Ar role
.Op Ar config...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility accepts a
.Xr ort 5
.Ar config
.Pq defaulting to standard input
and audits all access available to
.Ar role .
The output is rendered in the JSON format.
The configuration may be broken apart into several files.
.Pp
This tool is still experimental.
